if you didn't talk for a while.

80
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:56,960
Let me finish this off.

81
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:59,160
"You're my best friend in the world, Sam...

82
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:01,480
"...so you must know
that this is the way I am.

83
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:03,240
"l can't help it. It's my nature."

84
00:06:03,320 --> 00:06:05,440
It's true, son. She's nuts.

85
00:06:05,520 --> 00:06:07,800
