101
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:57,080
This better be goddamn good!

102
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:59,280
You're ruining my beauty sleep!

103
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:01,880
Damn you! Lay off the buzzer!

104
00:08:02,320 --> 00:08:04,080
Who is it?

105
00:08:05,840 --> 00:08:07,600
No problem here.

106
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:09,560
Who is it?

107
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:09,080
Morning, everybody.

108
00:10:09,160 --> 00:10:11,320
Morning, Linda. Morning, Tarzan.

109
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:15,200
We are...

110
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:17,880
...six minutes later than yesterday.

111
00:10:18,040 --> 00:10:21,400
That's six, carry the two. Good.

112
00:10:27,040 --> 00:10:28,120
Ah, there.

113
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,320
See that?

114
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:32,200
Medium smile, no teeth.

115
00:10:34,560 --> 00:10:36,400
Don't forget the vase.

116
00:10:36,560 --> 00:10:38,080
Got to get it perfectly centered.

117
