I feel sorry for you, you poor bastard.

125
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:23,960
Carl, it's me, Sam.

126
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:25,240
Calm down. I'm fine.

127
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:26,880
I'm still in New York.

128
00:11:28,040 --> 00:11:30,400
We're great. Linda's very happy.

129
00:11:31,160 --> 00:11:33,440
We may stay a while. We're very busy.

