158
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:18,600
I asked you a question.

159
00:17:24,440 --> 00:17:25,800
Don't touch that.

160
00:17:25,880 --> 00:17:27,760
Get away from that.

161
00:17:30,880 --> 00:17:33,280
Who the hell are you? What do you want?

162
00:17:34,400 --> 00:17:35,600
