It's the only way I'm comfortable.

172
00:18:23,400 --> 00:18:24,440
So don't think of it as a come-on...

173
00:18:24,520 --> 00:18:26,320
...because if you so much as breathe
in my direction...

174
00:18:26,400 --> 00:18:28,640
...Will nail your Willy to that beam.

175
00:18:30,240 --> 00:18:33,080
Don't mess with my stuff,
don't get in my way...

176
00:18:33,240 --> 00:18:36,160
...and I'm sure we'll get along fine.

177
00:18:36,320 --> 00:18:37,720
Nighty-night.

178
00:19:39,520 --> 00:19:41,360
What is all this stuff?

179
00:19:41,520 --> 00:19:43,440
